  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Backrooms: Lost Place</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single-player adventure horror game based on the Backrooms universe. The game combines puzzle, adventure, and horror mechanics. Dive into the fascinating and mysterious atmosphere of the Backrooms universe, playing as a student who accidentally finds himself in the Backrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/817398fc27e74f5c5eb5091a70954980.poster.avif?t=1734650390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/817398fc27e74f5c5eb5091a70954980.webm?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/817398fc27e74f5c5eb5091a70954980.mp4?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural generation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the levels in the game have procedural generation elements, which adds an element of replayability and interest to the playthroughs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/e52175be015dd43a873ddb3e42a5d7fa.poster.avif?t=1734650390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/e52175be015dd43a873ddb3e42a5d7fa.webm?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/e52175be015dd43a873ddb3e42a5d7fa.mp4?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Idea</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is not similar to other backrooms projects, as the game has no goal to scare you. There are elements of horror in the game, but the main idea is to explore and immerse all of us in our favorite world of backrooms. The game has a lot of puzzles and emphasis on visual aesthetics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/91ac6805cef2a8f62fd347d968db075d.poster.avif?t=1734650390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/91ac6805cef2a8f62fd347d968db075d.webm?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/91ac6805cef2a8f62fd347d968db075d.mp4?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Backrooms: Lost Place</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single-player adventure horror game based on the Backrooms universe. The game combines puzzle, adventure, and horror mechanics. Dive into the fascinating and mysterious atmosphere of the Backrooms universe, playing as a student who accidentally finds himself in the Backrooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/817398fc27e74f5c5eb5091a70954980.poster.avif?t=1734650390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/817398fc27e74f5c5eb5091a70954980.webm?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/817398fc27e74f5c5eb5091a70954980.mp4?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural generation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Most of the levels in the game have procedural generation elements, which adds an element of replayability and interest to the playthroughs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/e52175be015dd43a873ddb3e42a5d7fa.poster.avif?t=1734650390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/e52175be015dd43a873ddb3e42a5d7fa.webm?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/e52175be015dd43a873ddb3e42a5d7fa.mp4?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Idea</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is not similar to other backrooms projects, as the game has no goal to scare you. There are elements of horror in the game, but the main idea is to explore and immerse all of us in our favorite world of backrooms. The game has a lot of puzzles and emphasis on visual aesthetics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/91ac6805cef2a8f62fd347d968db075d.poster.avif?t=1734650390\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/91ac6805cef2a8f62fd347d968db075d.webm?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2420040/extras/91ac6805cef2a8f62fd347d968db075d.mp4?t=1734650390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
